### Transaction Event Sourcing Module - HTTP Requests
### Port: 8095
### Transaction + Event Sourcing Konuları (Event Store, Snapshot, Replay, Consistency)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8095
@contentType = application/json

### Event Store'a event kaydetme
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/eventsourcing/event
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "aggregateId": "order-123",
  "eventType": "OrderCreated",
  "eventData": "{\"orderNumber\":\"ORD-001\",\"amount\":1000.0}"
}

###

### Event Replay
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventsourcing/replay/order-123

###

### Snapshot oluşturma
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/eventsourcing/snapshot
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "aggregateId": "order-123",
  "snapshotData": "{\"orderNumber\":\"ORD-001\",\"amount\":1000.0,\"status\":\"PENDING\"}"
}

###


